---
const exhibitors = [
  { name: 'SAMPLE BIKES', url: '#', color: '#FF6B35' },
  { name: 'CAMP GEAR CO.', url: '#', color: '#00B4D8' },
  { name: 'TRAIL APPAREL', url: '#', color: '#FF6B6B' },
  { name: 'OUTDOOR LIFE', url: '#', color: '#0077B6' },
  { name: 'CYCLE WORKS', url: '#', color: '#FF8C61' },
  { name: 'GREEN TENT', url: '#', color: '#2D8F4E' },
  { name: 'FIRE SIDE', url: '#', color: '#E85D04' },
  { name: 'VELO CRAFT', url: '#', color: '#7B2CBF' },
];
---

<section id="exhibitors" class="exhibitors section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="exhibitors-header reveal">
      <span class="section-label">EXHIBITORS</span>
      <h2 class="exhibitors-title">
        <span class="gradient-text">出展ブランド</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="exhibitors-lead">
        ガレージブランドから有名ブランドまで、多彩な出展社が集結。<br class="pc-only">
        ロゴをクリックして各ブランドの詳細をチェック。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="exhibitors-grid">
      {exhibitors.map((ex, i) => (
        <a
          href={ex.url}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class={`exhibitor-card reveal delay-${(i % 4 + 1) * 100}`}
          title={ex.name}
        >
          <div class="exhibitor-logo" style={`--brand-color: ${ex.color}`}>
            <span class="exhibitor-initial">{ex.name.charAt(0)}</span>
          </div>
          <span class="exhibitor-name">{ex.name}</span>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>

    <p class="exhibitors-note reveal">
      ※ 出展社は随時追加されます。最新情報はSNSをご確認ください。
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .exhibitors {
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .exhibitors-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--color-sunset);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-label::before,
  .section-label::after {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 30px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-sunset);
    vertical-align: middle;
    margin: 0 1rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .exhibitors-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4.5vw, 2.8rem);
    color: var(--color-dark);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .exhibitors-lead {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .pc-only {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pc-only {
      display: inline;
    }
  }

  .exhibitors-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .exhibitors-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  .exhibitor-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-gray-100);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .exhibitor-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .exhibitor-logo {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color), color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-color) 70%, white));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .exhibitor-card:hover .exhibitor-logo {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-3deg);
  }

  .exhibitor-initial {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .exhibitor-name {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    text-align: center;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .exhibitor-card:hover .exhibitor-name {
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .exhibitors-note {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
  }
</style>
